21:35.495 --> 21:37.464
* You're pretty much amazing *

21:37.464 --> 21:40.333
* And you've been there for me *

21:40.333 --> 21:42.635
* Together we're beautiful *

21:42.635 --> 21:45.237
* I want you to stay *

