(exhausted gasping)

22:03.322 --> 22:05.892
* You're pretty much amazing *

22:05.892 --> 22:07.694
* Whoo-hoo *

22:07.694 --> 22:10.863
* You're pretty much amazing *

22:12.565 --> 22:15.101
* You're pretty much amazing *

22:15.101 --> 22:16.703
* Whoo-hoo... *

22:16.703 --> 22:19.739
I only had enough time
for 12 flying buttresses,

22:19.739 --> 22:22.174
but in actuality,
there are 26.

22:22.174 --> 22:23.943
* *

22:26.379 --> 22:28.715
"Then I'll be brief.
Oh, happy, dagger,

22:28.715 --> 22:30.016
Thank you, please.
"here is thy sheath.

22:30.016 --> 22:32.318
Thank you.
There rest and let me die."

22:32.318 --> 22:34.387
(sighs):
The show is Pippin,

22:34.387 --> 22:36.389
and I just wanted your name.

22:36.389 --> 22:39.592
(suppressed laughing)

22:39.592 --> 22:42.094
(laughter)
* I don't ever want it *

22:42.094 --> 22:44.731
* To end *

22:44.731 --> 22:47.500
* You're pretty much amazing *

22:47.500 --> 22:49.268
* Whoo-hoo *

22:49.268 --> 22:51.871
* You're pretty much amazing *

22:51.871 --> 22:54.273
* The way that you are *

22:54.273 --> 22:56.643
* You're pretty much amazing *

22:56.643 --> 22:58.611
* Whoo-hoo *

22:58.611 --> 23:00.647
* You're pretty much amazing *

23:00.647 --> 23:03.516
* While we're driving my car *

23:03.516 --> 23:05.217
* You're pretty much amazing *

23:05.217 --> 23:08.588
* You do it for me *

23:08.588 --> 23:11.123
Hey, baby, how you doing?!

